_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#qualifiedCardinality> "1"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger> .
_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <http://www.example.org/cedmar/#hasRiskClass> .
_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
<http://www.example.org/cedmar/#Device> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Instrument intended for medical purposes."@en .
